<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Wristband for Impaired Persons</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .head1 {
            background-color: #514848;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .features {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .feature-item {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 30%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .feature-item img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            height: 30vh;
        }
        .blogs {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .blog-post {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .blog-post h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

    
    <header class="head1">
        <h1>Wristband for Impaired Persons</h1>
        <p>Assistive Technology to Improve Lives</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <!-- Features Section -->
        <section class="features">
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h2>Vibration Alerts</h2>
                <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.lUhEQl95bn8PPtlEXc7xagAAAA?w=257&h=180&c=7&r=0&o=5&dpr=1.3&pid=1.7" alt="Vibration Alerts">
                <p>The wristband provides vibration-based alerts for notifications like calls or messages, ideal for hearing-impaired individuals.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h2>GPS Tracking</h2>
                <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.VbEXgumClHsVf4Lh9ZdXQAHaEK?w=324&h=182&c=7&r=0&o=5&dpr=1.3&pid=1.7" alt="GPS Tracking">
                <p>Equipped with GPS, it helps in locating the wearer, providing peace of mind for caregivers and family members.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h2>Emergency SOS Button</h2>
                <a href=""onclick="callEmergency()" class="sos-button"><img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.VhrJPS5i6uRjjlRbruHHgAAAAA?w=328&h=184&c=7&r=0&o=5&dpr=1.3&pid=1.7" alt="Emergency SOS">
                   
                    </a>
                <p>A quick-press emergency button that sends out an alert to predefined contacts in case of emergency.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Blog Section -->
        <section class="blogs">
            <h2>Latest Blogs</h2>

            <div class="blog-post">
                <h3>How Wristbands Improve Daily Life for the Hearing-Impaired</h3>
                <p>The latest advancements in wearable technology provide life-saving features and daily convenience for those with hearing loss...</p>
                <a href="#">Read More</a>
            </div>

            <div class="blog-post">
                <h3>GPS Tracking: Safety & Peace of Mind for Families</h3>
                <p>Learn how GPS-enabled wristbands are helping families stay connected to their loved ones, especially those with disabilities...</p>
                <a href="#">Read More</a>
            </div>

            <div class="blog-post">
                <h3>5 Features to Look For in an Assistive Wristband</h3>
                <p>Finding the right assistive wristband for a loved one can be challenging. Here's a breakdown of the top features you should consider...</p>
                <a href="#">Read More</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    

</body>
</html>